node.text:
DNF 🇭🇺🏁

I had a tricky start and I made a mistake in the damp conditions judging the braking, leaving it too late. It destroyed my race and many other driver’s race as well. Not ideal at all, but we live and learn. Time for a break and to recharge for a stronger 2nd half of the season!

Congrats @estebanocon for the first win! And great to see @lewishamilton fight back to the podium to get some important points for us.

#VB77 #F1 #HungarianGP
@mercedesamgf1 @f1 
📷 @kymillman + @thomas_maheux
